{
  "openapi": "3.0.3",
  "info": {
    "title": "Keepcon API",
    "description": "app_keepcon 对外 HTTP 接口（长连接推送：服务端经 Channels 向已鉴权 WebSocket 客户端投递消息）。\n\n- **挂载前缀**：`/api/keepcon/`（见 `service_foundation/urls.py`）。\n- **响应包络**：`{ errorCode, data, message, ... }`；`errorCode === 0` 表示成功（与 `common.pojo.response.Response` / `resp_ok`一致）。多数错误在业务层仍返回 **HTTP 200**，通过 `errorCode` 区分。\n- **请求 ID**：可传请求头 `X-Request-Id`；成功响应由 `response_with_request_id` 写入响应头（默认名 `X-Request-Id`，可由 `REQUEST_ID_RESPONSE_HEADER` 覆盖）。\n- **WebSocket**（非 OpenAPI 路径）：浏览器/终端连接 `ws(s)://<host>/ws/keepcon/`。鉴权后客户端加入组 `keepcon_{device_key}`（逻辑组名；Redis 中 Channels key 另带配置前缀）。JSON 消息类型概要：`hello`（`device_key` + `secret`）→ `hello_ok` / `hello_fail`；`sync`（`since_seq`）→ `sync_ok`；`ack`（`msg_id`）→ `ack_ok`；`ping` → `pong`；下行 `push`（`msg_id`, `seq`, `payload`）。",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "/",
      "description": "相对当前站点根路径"
    }
  ],
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "Keepcon",
      "description": "健康检查与内部消息投递"
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/api/keepcon/health": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["Keepcon"],
        "summary": "健康检查",
        "operationId": "keepconHealth",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "成功",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "allOf": [
                    { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/EnvelopeOk" },
                    {
                      "type": "object",
                      "properties": {
                        "data": {
                          "type": "object",
                          "properties": {
                            "status": { "type": "string", "example": "ok" },
                            "service": { "type": "string", "example": "keepcon" }
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            },
            "headers": {
              "X-Request-Id": { "$ref": "#/components/headers/XRequestId" },
              "Expires": { "schema": { "type": "string" } }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/keepcon/internal/messages": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Keepcon"],
        "summary": "内部投递消息到设备",
        "description": "供已注册的 HTTP 调用方（`reg.access_key`，且 **status=启用**，与 `ServiceRegStatus.ENABLED` 一致）向指定 `device_key` 投递 `payload`：落库为待推送消息并 `group_send` 到对应 WebSocket 组；无在线客户端时消息仍为 pending。\n\n- `payload`：可为任意 JSON 可序列化值；非 object/array 时会包装为 `{\"value\": ...}` 再序列化存储。\n- **幂等**：`idem_key` 与 `idempotency_key` 二选一（字符串，去空白）；相同键复用已存在消息，返回该消息的 `msg_id` / `seq` / `status`。\n- 常见 `message`：`access_key is required`、`invalid or inactive access_key`、`device_key is required`、`payload is required`、`device not found or disabled`（均为参数类错误，`errorCode` 为 100）。未捕获的服务器异常可能由统一异常中间件处理（HTTP 状态码或非 0 `errorCode` 以实际为准）。",
        "operationId": "keepconInternalDispatch",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/InternalDispatchRequest" },
              "examples": {
                "minimal": {
                  "summary": "最简投递",
                  "value": {
                    "access_key": "YOUR_ACCESS_KEY",
                    "device_key": "device_001",
                    "payload": { "type": "notify", "text": "hello" }
                  }
                },
                "withIdempotency": {
                  "summary": "带幂等键",
                  "value": {
                    "access_key": "YOUR_ACCESS_KEY",
                    "device_key": "device_001",
                    "payload": { "order_id": "o1" },
                    "idem_key": "idem-2025-001"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "成功或参数/业务校验错误（errorCode≠0 时 HTTP 常为 200，见包络）",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "oneOf": [
                    {
                      "allOf": [
                        { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/EnvelopeOk" },
                        {
                          "type": "object",
                          "properties": {
                            "data": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/DispatchResult" }
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/EnvelopeError" }
                  ]
                }
              }
            },
            "headers": {
              "X-Request-Id": { "$ref": "#/components/headers/XRequestId" }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "components": {
    "headers": {
      "XRequestId": {
        "description": "请求关联 ID；客户端可传 `X-Request-Id`，响应会回显。",
        "schema": { "type": "string" }
      }
    },
    "schemas": {
      "EnvelopeOk": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["errorCode", "message"],
        "properties": {
          "errorCode": { "type": "integer", "enum": [0], "description": "成功为 0" },
          "data": { "description": "业务数据" },
          "message": { "type": "string", "description": "成功时通常为空串" }
        }
      },
      "EnvelopeError": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["errorCode", "message"],
        "properties": {
          "errorCode": { "type": "integer", "description": "非 0；本接口参数/鉴权失败为 100（RET_INVALID_PARAM）" },
          "data": { "nullable": true },
          "message": { "type": "string" },
          "detail": { "type": "string" },
          "_req_id": { "type": "string" }
        }
      },
      "InternalDispatchRequest": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["access_key", "device_key", "payload"],
        "properties": {
          "access_key": {
            "type": "string",
            "minLength": 1,
            "description": "调用方在 keepcon `reg` 表中的 access_key，且记录须为启用状态。"
          },
          "device_key": {
            "type": "string",
            "minLength": 1,
            "description": "目标设备键；设备须存在且启用（status=1）。"
          },
          "payload": {
            "description": "投递给客户端的业务负载；须出现该键；值可为 object、array、标量等（标量会按实现包装后存库）。"
          },
          "idem_key": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "幂等键；与 `idempotency_key` 等价，优先使用先出现的非空值。"
          },
          "idempotency_key": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "同 `idem_key`。"
          }
        }
      },
      "DispatchResult": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["msg_id", "seq", "device_key", "status"],
        "properties": {
          "msg_id": { "type": "integer", "description": "消息主键" },
          "seq": { "type": "integer", "description": "设备维度单调序号" },
          "device_key": { "type": "string" },
          "status": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "消息状态：0=pending，1=delivered，2=acked（新建成功时一般为 0）",
            "enum": [0, 1, 2]
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
